
1  Ruoth Nyasaye wacho niya, “Un jo-Israel, ka uyie lokoru, to duoguru ira. Wituru nyisecheu manono ma Amon-go mondo uluw mana an. 
2  Ka ukuong’oru gi nying Ruoth Nyasaye gi adiera gi bura makare kendo gi tim malong’o, to ogendini biro kwaya mondo gin bende aguedhgi kaka aseguedhou, kendo gibiro miya duong’. 
3  

Ruoth Nyasaye wacho ni jo-Juda gi jo-Jerusalem niya, ‘Paruru puotheu ma mbora, mondo kik uket kodhi e kind kudho. 
4  Un jo-Juda gi jo-Jerusalem, rituru singruokna, kendo timuru gik madwaro, nono to gik maricho musetimo biro miyo mirimba liel ka mach ma onge ng’ama nyalo nego.’

Onyis jo-Juda ni wasigu biro monjogi


5  “Gouru tung’, e piny duto, kendo koguru matek, kunyiso jo-Juda gi jo-Jerusalem mondo oring odhi e mier mochiel motegno. 
6  Nyisuru ji yo madhi Sayun. Ringuru mondo utony, kik udeki, nikech Ruoth Nyasaye kelo masira kaa nyandwat mabiro ketho piny malich. 
7  Jaketh ogendini osewuok oko ka sibuor mowuok e gonde. Osewuok kama odakie mondo obi oketh pinyu. Miech Juda nodong’ gundni ma onge ng’ama odakie. 
8  Kuom mano, rwakreuru gi piende gugru, kendo uywagi ka ugoyo nduru, nikech mirima mager ma Ruoth Nyasaye nigo gi jo-Juda pok orumo.”


9  Ruoth Nyasaye nowacho niya, “Chieng’no chuny ruodhi gi chuny jodongo nonyosre, kata jodolo bende nobuogi kendo jonabi nong’eng’.” 
10  Kane awinjo kamano, nawacho niya, “A Ruoth Nyasaye, isewuondo jo-Jerusalem chuth! Niwacho ni kue biro betie, to koro ligangla ema nie ng’utwa!”


11  Ndalo biro, mibiro nyisie jo-Jerusalem ni yamo maliet moa e thim kudho koni, kochomo jo-Ruoth Nyasaye. Ok nokudh mos maber minyalo piedhgo cham, 
12  to nobed kalausi ma Ruoth Nyasaye okelo. Ruoth Nyasaye owuon ema koro kumo joge.


13  Neuru, wasigu biro mogingore ka boche polo. Gechegi mag lweny chalo gi kalausi, kendo faresegi ringo matek moloyo ongo. Yaye! Warumo! 
14  Un jo-Jerusalem, lwokuru richo manie chunyu mondo oresu. Ubiro siko kuparo weche maricho nyaka karang’o? 
15  Winjuru! Jaote moa Dan ema hulo ni masira biro, kendo jago milome moa e gode mag Efraim bende wacho kamano. 
16  Nyisuru ogendini kendo landuru wach ni, Jerusalem ibiro kethi. Wasigu biro moa e piny mabor, kendo gibiro goyo koko ni joma odak e miech Juda. 
17  Gibiro timo ageng’a ni piny Juda mana ka joma olworo puodho, nikech oganda jo-Juda oseweya. Ruoth Nyasaye ema owacho kamano.


18  “Un jo-Juda, un ema usekelo masira kuomu uwegi, nikech yoreu gi timbeu maricho. Ee, richou ema okelonu masira kum malitni.”


19  Iya nyawni! Awinjo rem malit! Yaye chunya! Chunya diko malit! Ok anyal ling’ nikech awinjo tung’ gi mahu mag lweny. 
20  Masira achiel luwo machielo, kendo piny duto okethi, piyopiyo nono hembena omuki, kendo rageng’ni maggi oyiech matindo tindo. 
21  Nyaka karang’o ma ananeye bandeche mag lweny ka kwadhore, kendo nawinjie tung’ lweny ka ywak.


22  Ruoth Nyasaye wacho niya, “Joga ofuwo, kendo ok ging’eya. Gichalo gi nyithindo momemore, kendo maonge rieko. Richo ema ging’eyo timo, to timo gima ber otamogi.”


23  Bang’e narango piny, maneno ni onge gi kido. Polo bende ne onge gima rienyie. 
24  Ne arango gode madongo, maneno ka giyiengni; kuonde moting’ore bende ne rundore koni gi koni. 
25  Naneno ka ji onge kuno, kendo winy duto noseringo. 
26  Piny momew noselokore thim, kendo mier man kuno noselokore gundni, nikech mirima mager mar Ruoth Nyasaye. 
27  Ruoth Nyasaye osewacho ni piny ngima biro dong’ nono, to ok nokethe chuth. 
28  Ji duto modak e piny noywagi, kendo polo nolokre mudho. Ruoth Nyasaye osewacho, kendo ok nolok parone! Oseparo mogik, kendo ok nodog chien. 
29  Ka ji winjo ni joidh farese gi jo asere biro, to ng’ato ka ng’ato noringi. Jomoko noring odhi e bunge, to moko noidh lwendni, mi pond kuno. Mier duto nodong’ nono, ma onge ng’ama odakie. 
30  Un jo-Jerusalem, urumo! Ere gimomiyo urwakoru gi lewni mabeyo, koso ere gima omiyo urwako stadi kendo uwiro wengeu? Ubisoru maber kayiem nono, to chodeu oseweyou, kendo koro dwaro negou. 
31  Ne awinjo ywak ka mar dhako ma muoch kayo. Ee, mana kaka mar dhako ma hango nywol. Kara ne en mana dwond Jerusalem, ma gamo yueyo, kendo orieyo bade kawacho niya, “Arumo! Chunya dwaro a, nikech jonek lwora mondo onega.”

